{"tid":462936,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺不覺某台好多人都有呢個病？","createTime":"2017-11-09T04:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T04:47:47.000Z","uid":17606,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"19f566924ea7516a8614f8f48df64929c4594349","tid":462936,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"被害妄想型<br />\n<br />\n「妄想」是指病人整天多疑多慮，胡亂推理和判斷，思維發生障礙，是精神疾病的一個重要癥狀。患者可伴有幻覺，但無其他明顯的精神癥狀。病人由於缺乏安全感，導致對外界的極度不信任，而產生的一種幻想。多發於老年人或者某些曾經受過超出自我承受能力範圍的打擊的人。<br />\n<br />\n病人會無中生有地堅信某人（或某群體）對自己、自己的親人、家庭，進行監視、攻擊或迫害。被害妄想是妄想症中最常見的一種。患者往往處於恐懼狀態，感覺被人議論、誣陷，遭人暗算，財產被劫，被人強姦等。被害妄想往往有自殺及謀殺企圖，如不早診斷及早治療易釀成大禍。"},{"pid":"61026c104ea184017c82f40ba3d265f15bcb8f0b","tid":462936,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2d8abdb28eec477e24ee86ada82c30061f24ab","tid":462936,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:34:33.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"0161a44452a3c724b41b4b96593e215e13d8ce4f","tid":462936,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"cc台"},{"pid":"7d417cff0d253bf05169e30811f35f83f4e13aea","tid":462936,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"波台狗係咁"},{"pid":"32741c3a11e3ea563fd0b43bd6dbe1d315a548d6","tid":462936,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"成日話麻友係g嗰班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa12c30ed41be4c5f14eeec9f435236c0b433012","tid":462936,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日話麻友係g嗰班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSu膠吉勞"},{"pid":"0d111faa084845c6ab606f568e40715284832bf8","tid":462936,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,